text:
Ro: Hey guys, it’s Ro, I’m here with my
sister Mo today.
Mo: Hey Everybody!

Ro: And, we asked you guys which game we should
play next

Ro: and we got so many requests for… Mo:
The Hamburger Challenge!

Ro: Yep, and for those of you who don’t
know, the Hamburger Challenge is where

Ro: the both of us will be blindfolded and we
have to take a

Ro: bite of the burger blindfolded and guess
which fast food restaurant it came from.

Ro: And, we had our friends go out to 6 different
fast food restaurants and
Ro: we’re gonna be keeping score.
Ro: Let’s get started!

Ro: 1st thing we gotta do is put on our blind
folds, got these awesome aviator

Ro: blindfolds, Mo let’s put these on. Mo:
They’re pretty fancy, here we go!

Ro: OK, so we can’t see anything. Ow! OK,
there!

Ro: How’s that? How’s that? Pretty good?
How’s my hair look?
Mo: Um… Pretty good!

Ro: Great! I can’t see anything, let’s
get this goin!

Mo: Oh I’m excited! Ro: I can haz cheeseburgers!
Mo: Om nom nom nom nom nom!
Mo: Alright, here’s the 1st burger.
Ro: OK, I gotta unwrap it.

Ro: Which restaurant had seeds on the top,
I don’t know.
Ro: Alright, are you ready to take a bite?
Mo: I just did… Ro: Oh my gosh!
Mo: I was really hungry, sorry.

Ro: So on 3, we are gonna guess what kind
of burger this is at the same time.
Ro: Are you ready? Mo: Yeah!
Both: Jack in the Box!
Mo: Oh-hahaha OK! Yeah!
Ro: OK, lets see, how’d we do?

Mo: Nooo, wait! Ro: Carls Jr. Mo: Oh darn
it! Ro: Oh stinker!

Ro: Alright! Off to a good start! Mo: Woo
hoo!

Mo: That was pretty good. Ro: I’m gonna
have another bite! Mo: Mmmhmm!
Ro: Ooooh OK, 2nd burger, here we go!
Ro: Oooh it’s smaller. Mo: Mmmhmm.
Ro: Oh a smooth bun. Mo: Mmmhmm, you ready?
Ro: OK, OK.
Ro: Tsa-tsa-tsa-tsa-tsa…

Ro: I’m just gonna have to eat this whole
thing, I can’t figure it out.
Both: McDonalds!

Mo: Shut the front door, that’s what I said
too! Ro: Oh my gosh are we related?
Ro: Are we related?

Mo: OK, let’s check, let’s check! Ro:
OK, ready?

Ro: Wendy’s! Mo: Oh it’s Wendy’s. 0
for 2!
Mo: Onto the next burger! Ro: Next burger!

Ro: Oh my! Mo: It’s big! Ro: It’s a big
burger!
Ro: It’s got a little skirt on it.
Ro: OK, 1, 2…

Ro: Mmmm! I know that taste anywhere! Are
you ready?
Mo: Jack in the Box! Ro: In-N-Out!

Mo: Oh, is it? I’m gonna look. Ro: OK ready?
Let’s look.
Mo: Oh OK, you got it! Ro: IN-N-OUT!!!! Yes!

Ro: Oh yeah! Mmmm! This is like the best challenge
game ever.
Mo: Cheers to that! Ro: Mmmhmmm!

Ro: Point for me, 1st point of the day, we’re
gonna display it right here.
Mo: Burger number 4!

Mo: This is wrapped very nice! Ro: This is
very nice wrapping!
Ro: Oop, oop! It’s falling apart!

Ro: Did you take a bite yet? Mo: Mmmhmm! Ro:
Oh-oh!

Mo: OK, are you ready? Ro: No! Let me just
take another bite just to be sure!

Mo: Another bite? Ro: It’s a science Molly!
Mo: Oh OK… Ro: You can’t rush it!
Both: Jack in the box!

Mo: It’s Burger King… Ro: Bahahahaha!
Mo: Dang it! Ro: We do not know our burgers

Ro: Molly, this is embarrassing! Mo: It’s
pretty good though!
Ro: I’m just gonna go behind here! Hahahaha!

Mo: You know, if I just keep guessing Jack
in the Box it’s gonna be right

Mo: 1 of these times. Ro: Hee-hee-hee! Mo:
I think…
Ro: Hey little burg. Mo: Here we go!

Mo: Mmmhmm! I think I know this one, I actually
think I know this one!

Ro: I think these are what I used to eat in
high school.

Mo: OK, OK, so are you ready? Ro: And the
number 2 on the menu!

Mo: 1… Ro: Let me see if I’m right. Mo:
2, 3…
Both: McDonalds!

Mo: The 1st point! Yeah! Ro: Woop woop, woop
woop!

Ro: Can you tie this up? Can you make this
a tie win?

Mo: Everything is riding on this round. Ro:
This is THE round Molly!

Mo: This is, this is it! Ro: OK, here we go!
Mo: Burger number 6!
Ro: Oh another smooth bun…

Mo: The bun is kind of sweet, I think the
bun is sweeter than the rest.

Ro: The burger tastes more grill-y… Mo:
Hmmmm.

Ro: This ones really important so I need to
take another bite so I don’t lose!
Mo: OK.

Mo: Oh my gosh, what is, what is taking so
long? Are you ready?

Ro: Molly, I'm... This is really important, I need
to take my time,
Ro: to really do my research here.

Mo: Well I guess just let me know, haha, when
you’re ready then…

Ro: OK, I think I get it… Wait… Let me
do… Mo, where’s the burger?

Ro: Let me do some more research. Mo: No,
oh! Ro: Let me do a little bit more research.
Mo: Hey! Ro: Hmmm-hmmm-hmmm-hmmm!
Ro: Arby’s! Mo: Jack in the Box!
Mo: OK, let’s check, let’s check!

Mo: Ohhhhhhh! Ro: Oh Molly! It’s your Jack
in the Box!
Mo: We tied!

Ro: Oh! We… A tie win, this has never happened
before to us.
Ro: Oh my god that’s bacon! Mo: Yeah, give... Ro: No wonder I liked that so much!
Mo: Yeah, that was a really good one!
Mo: Ta-da! Ro: Da-dewww!

Ro: 1st time in history we have ever had a
tie challenge game! Mo: Woooooo!

Ro: We tied, good game! Mo: Good game! Ro:
Good game sister, good sportsmanship.
Mo: Well played!

Ro: If you guys have any other ideas of any
other games we should play together,

Ro: Let us know, leave us a comment down below
and if you guys play

Ro: The Hamburger Challenge game, let us know
in the comments what your favorite
Ro: burgers was. Mo: Mmmmmm!

Ro: What was your favorite burger, do you
remember?

Mo: I really liked the last one with bacon.
Ro: That was really good!

Ro: Also, if you want to see any other vlogs
you can click up here. Mo: Or up here!
Ro: Yeah to check ‘em out!

Ro: And I will be putting Mo’s links down
below, she has a Twitter and Instagram!

Ro: Yeah so if you want to see any cool pictures
that she posts, those will be ‘dere!

Ro: OK, thanks again you guys, bye-bye! Mo:
Bye!

Ro: You can pick your friends, but you can’t
pick your friends’ nose…
Ro: Tee-hee! See!?

Mo: I knew that was coming! Ro: A-hahaha!
Mo: I Know you!
Ro: You know me!?!? Mo: A-haha I know you!
Ro: How do you know me!?!?! A-hahahaha!

Ro: As your sister I can see what you’re
thinking through your eyes!

Mo: What am I thinking right now? Ro: That
my hair’s cray but you’re not telling me!
Mo: I was thinking about that last burger!
Both: Hahahahaha!
